    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>The effects of your bardic performance carry on, even after you have stopped performing.</em></p><p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Bardic performance class feature.</p><p><strong>Benefit</strong>: The bonuses and penalties from your bardic performance continue for 2 rounds after you cease performing. Any other requirement, such as range or specific conditions, must still be met for the effect to continue. If you begin a new bardic performance during this time, the effects of the previous performance immediately cease.</p>"
